<h2>Overview: What You Will Need</h2>
<p><strong>Time required:</strong> 30 to 60 minutes for initial setup. Ongoing content optimization.</p>
<p><strong>Difficulty:</strong> Intermediate</p>
<p><strong>What you will need:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Access to your website's <code>robots.txt</code> file</li>
<li>A Google Analytics 4 account</li>
<li>Content management system access</li>
<li>Existing content to optimize (or the ability to publish new content)</li>
